title: 19th Summerschool in Immunotoxicology
location: Radisson Hotel Vieux Port, Marseille, France
extranight:
Early bird registration is now closed. From 1 July, normal registration fees (2,400 euros) are applicable. The very final registration deadline is  6 August 2010.

Registration fees include full accommodation during the whole of summerschool (2 nights). Thus, any extra-night should be booked and paid directly to Radisson Hotel Vieux Port (with room reservation form which you can find in the documents section).

If you cannot attend after registration, a substitute delegate may attend in your place. In case of cancellation prior to 1 August 2010, 90% of the fees will be returned;  prior to 25 August 2010, 50% will be returned. After this date, no refund will be made.
